		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- Surely, but I'd like to know how $2004 works on reads. The wiki says that <em>reading OAMDATA while the PPU is rendering will expose internal OAM accesses during sprite evaluation and loading</em>. What if the screen isn't rendering?
<br />
<br />- Defined <strong>rendering</strong> as background or sprites enabled, between scanlines 0 and 239 (here it's 21 and 260).

		

		</td>
