		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Zepper wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What if the screen isn't rendering?</div>
<br />During vertical blanking or with rendering turned off at PPUMASK, it just returns the contents of OAM[OAMADDR] <em>without</em> incrementing OAMADDR.

		

		</td>
